articles.title: Oakland Ballers to use artificial intelligence to manage Saturday home game against Great Falls
articles.summary: The playoff-bound Ballers of the independent Pioneer League are turning to AI to manage most aspects of Saturday’s home game against the Great Falls Voyagers at Raimondi Park.

articles.title: Warner Bros. Sues Midjourney for AI-Generated Images of Superman, Bugs Bunny and Other Characters
